ğŸ§  How the Multi-Agent System Works

Each agent is a separate Python class:

ExplainerAgent â†’ explains concepts

QuizAgent â†’ creates quizzes

SummarizerAgent â†’ summarizes text

Chat Mode â†’ interacts using PDF + memory + Google AI

Routing is handled inside app.py:

